text.tspan: From Ojee07 Productions we thank
you for playing Netherlandsball: United
Provinces! This game is a fictional,
lighthearted grand strategy experience
inspired by projects such as games by
SHN Games, Risk, and Hearts of Iron IV.
In this alternate history, the Netherlands
faces a collapse in 1986, where its
provinces break away into separate
states, each with a goal of reuniting the
nation. Please note that all events and
outcomes within this game are entirely
fictional and should not be taken as a
reflection of real history. This is just an
exploration of an imagined scenario as
a tribute to my Country. Special thanks
to my talented girlfriend RobloxPandaYT,
Who drew the hats for the Provinces!
All music and additional art assets used
within the game are sourced from
copyright-free material, ensuring a
legally sound and enjoyable experience.
Have fun re-uniting the Netherlands!
